definition: Italy/Italian/abbr. for 意大利[Yi4 da4 li4]

sentences.english: There are also the paedophile tendencies in your subconscious?
sentences.chinese: 在你的潛意識裏，也存在的戀童傾向？

sentences.english: But he doesn't think the presence was something his subconscious conjured.
sentences.chinese: 但他不認爲他的存在是一些別有用心的潛意識。

sentences.english: The exercise merely helps to impress that mental image on your subconscious mind.
sentences.chinese: 體育鍛煉只能幫助你將精神願景印入你的潛意識之中。

sentences.english: This determination will put your subconscious to work and steer you towards success.
sentences.chinese: 這樣的決心會使你的潛意識驅使着你向成功前進。

sentences.english: P122: The unconscious thinks in terms of content and structure.
sentences.chinese: 潛意識以內容和結構來思考。

sentences.english: I am not self-consciously generating a pattern of statistical frequencies.
sentences.chinese: 我潛意識中會產生一種統計上的頻率模式。

sentences.english: You have carried it with you in successive incarnations, albeit in your subconsciousness.
sentences.chinese: 你們在前世已經攜帶它，在你的潛意識中。

sentences.english: I go to my subconsciousness. I have to go into that chaos.
sentences.chinese: 我要進入到我的潛意識裏。

sentences.english: We unconsciously assume the center of a picture corresponds to a fulcrum.
sentences.chinese: 我們的潛意識中認爲一幅圖的中心是一個支點。

sentences.english: Following that you must remain immersed in aiming while your subconscious controls the rhomboid tightening.
sentences.chinese: 你必須控制瞄準，潛意識裏，菱形肌肉連續用力。

sentences.english: The concept of modern Sub conciousness must be applied for studying the mind philosophy of Taosim.
sentences.chinese: 深入研究道家精神哲學，必須引入現代潛意識概念。

sentences.english: If I could see the unconscious, it'd be conscious.
sentences.chinese: 如果潛意識被看見，那麼它就是意識的。

sentences.english: We should look on Freud's subconsciousness theory dialectically.
sentences.chinese: 對弗洛伊德潛意識理論必須加以辯證的看待。

sentences.english: When we are studying the best within ourselves, we are potentially prescribing.
sentences.chinese: 研究我們當中最優秀的個體時，我們潛意識裏在學習。

sentences.english: The subconscious can consider all perspectives put together and atthe same time.
sentences.chinese: 潛意識中可以同時考慮所有觀點。

sentences.english: The unccious is the unwritten history of mankind from time unrecorded.
sentences.chinese: 潛意識是未曾付諸文本的人類洪荒時代史。

definition: lit. that person/fig. the person you have been looking for/Mr Right/the girl of one's dreams
